{"tid":1304461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】大埔「連儂隧道」警撕走含警員資料紙張　稱違私隱例恐嚇作為    未經准許而展示招貼","createTime":"2019-07-10T15:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:39:39.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ffba46056d5199eb66a1443aa5c340a37b793065","tid":1304461,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:22:32.000Z","msg":"【逃犯條例】大埔「連儂隧道」警撕走含警員資料紙張　稱違私隱例<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，張貼這些單張除可能干犯《個人資料(私隱)條例》第64條，亦可能違反《刑事罪行條例》第24條禁止某些恐嚇作為；或《公眾衛生及市政條例》第104A條禁止未經准許而展示招貼或海報等。警方亦會考慮把涉及警務人員個人資料被披露的個案轉交個人資料私隱專員公署跟進。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190710/s00001/1562735936921/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E3%80%8C%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%93%E3%80%8D%E8%AD%A6%E6%92%95%E8%B5%B0%E5%90%AB%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E7%B4%99%E5%BC%B5-%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%95%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E4%BE%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190710%2Fs00001%2F1562735936921%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E9%259A%25A7%25E9%2581%2593%25E3%2580%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2592%2595%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E5%2590%25AB%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25E7%25B4%2599%25E5%25BC%25B5-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%2581%2595%25E7%25A7%2581%25E9%259A%25B1%25E4%25BE%258B&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3cIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=b2f51a4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190710%2Fs00001%2F1562735936921%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E9%259A%25A7%25E9%2581%2593%25E3%2580%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2592%2595%25E8